project:
Version 22
Originally made for
[color=#ff004d]TOY BOX JAM 3[/color] by [color=#29adff]Lasermagnet Games[/color]

Controls:

W/A/S/D: move quadcopter
  SPACE: use beam / select blueprint
      Q: cycle blueprints

      F: toggle full screen mode
      M: toggle audio
      P: pause/resume

Gamepad, mouse and touch input are also supported.
